# ZeroLinux CODEOWNERS
# Reviewers are automatically assigned based on changed paths.
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything
*                   @zerolinux/maintainers

# Core framework — requires maintainer review
/core/              @zerolinux/maintainers
/bin/               @zerolinux/maintainers
install.sh          @zerolinux/maintainers
uninstall.sh        @zerolinux/maintainers

# Security-sensitive files
SECURITY.md         @zerolinux/maintainers
doctor.sh           @zerolinux/maintainers

# Plugins — can be reviewed by contributors
/plugins/           @zerolinux/maintainers @zerolinux/contributors

# Docs
/docs/              @zerolinux/maintainers
README.md           @zerolinux/maintainers
CONTRIBUTING.md     @zerolinux/maintainers

# CI
/.github/           @zerolinux/maintainers
